 is a variant of the }{\b\insrsid7345968 Peak Works for Windows}{\insrsid7345968  program developed by the HNU Systems / PID Analyzers, together with an interface 
device to receive analog data from and to communicate with a gas chromatograph. This variant of the program can be installed in a desktop or a laptop computer, and analog signals from any gas chromatograph can be sent to the analog inputs of the }{
\b\insrsid7345968 Integrator}{\insrsid7345968 . There are also several digital input and output lines at the }{\b\insrsid7345968 Integrator}{\insrsid7345968  that allow a handshaking between the }{\b\insrsid7345968 Integrator}{\insrsid7345968 
 and the Gas Chromatograph.  The }{\b\insrsid7345968 WPEAK Computing Integrator}{\insrsid7345968  performs data acquisition, processing, displaying, and storing the results to the hard drive of the PC. 
